The Arni Magnusson Institute's submission comprises a pipeline of four translation models and a grammar correction model, which have been trained on carefully curated datasets \citep{ami:2024}. These partly include synthetic data, generated using an LLM, and we find that it increases the translation capability of our system significantly.


